[{"question":"What is the purpose of Christmas?","answer":"Well, you know, the angels in the story of the first Christmas said three things.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":34,"aSentId":35},{"question":"Really?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":75,"aSentId":76},{"question":"And do you get people from all religions?","answer":"Oh, of course.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":78,"aSentId":79},{"question":"-- or a Jew or whoever it may be?","answer":"Well, we\u0027re an overtly Christian church.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":87,"aSentId":88},{"question":"But why do you think it\u0027s on the decline?","answer":"Well, I think there are three different factors.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":109,"aSentId":110},{"question":"Do you like the extraordinary position of responsibility you now have -- now have for yourself?","answer":"I don\u0027t say that I like it, but I try to use it.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":220,"aSentId":221},{"question":"-- is it healthy?","answer":"Well, no, it\u0027s not healthy.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":289,"aSentId":290},{"question":"And they then devote a large chunk of that to helping needy people, people less fortunate than themselves, does that balance it out?","answer":"ARREN: Well, the studies show, no, it doesn\u0027t.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":297,"aSentId":298},{"question":"Have you had big problems in that marriage, if you like?","answer":"Oh, absolutely.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":330,"aSentId":331},{"question":"Do people give up on marriage too early these days?","answer":"I think so.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":361,"aSentId":362},{"question":"They don\u0027t fight enough for it?","answer":"Well, and -- and the problem is, you\u0027re an imperfect person and you\u0027re going to marry an imperfect person.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":364,"aSentId":365},{"question":"How many times have you been properly in love?","answer":"OK.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":410,"aSentId":411},{"question":"Rick, how many times have you been properly in love in your life?","answer":"Well, probably in my teenage years, I fell in love every week.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":416,"aSentId":417},{"question":"-- it feels completely natural?","answer":"Oh, it\u0027s not only natural, it\u0027s euphoric.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":431,"aSentId":432},{"question":"What -- why can you not allow them to have that euphoria that you had, with all the rights that go with that kind of relationship?","answer":"Great question.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":443,"aSentId":444},{"question":"Can I pull that back?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":467,"aSentId":468},{"question":"-- supporting and voting and making legal gay marriage?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":503,"aSentId":504},{"question":"-- it is just wrong?","answer":"Well...","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":507,"aSentId":508},{"question":"Or could you see a time when you may say, you know something, America has changed, I\u0027m prepared to change?","answer":"I don\u0027t see that happening, because I have a world view based on scripture that remains unchanged.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":509,"aSentId":510},{"question":"What does being free mean?","answer":"No, no, nobody -- you can love anybody you want to in our freedom...","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":559,"aSentId":560},{"question":"But what is freedom?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":566,"aSentId":567},{"question":"Is that if -- if a mean -- a word means a certain thing, and it\u0027s not -- and it\u0027s not my word and all of a sudden I say, well, I\u0027m that, is that fair?","answer":"You...","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":581,"aSentId":582},{"question":"So you wouldn\u0027t have amended anything to the Constitution?","answer":"I\u0027m -- I\u0027m not sure what you\u0027re saying.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":584,"aSentId":585},{"question":"You think everything in the Bible is completely accurate?","answer":"I think the Bible is true; not everything in the Bible that is explained in the Bible does the Bible commend.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":616,"aSentId":617},{"question":"How do you try and change the fact that Christmas becomes this crystallization for many people of all that\u0027s terrible in their lives?","answer":"Right.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":670,"aSentId":671},{"question":"Really?","answer":"It is a tradition we call Birthday Party for Jesus.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":682,"aSentId":683},{"question":"Do you know how much you\u0027re worth?","answer":"No.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":723,"aSentId":724},{"question":"He\u0027s an impressive guy, isn\u0027t he?","answer":"He is.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":760,"aSentId":761},{"question":"How do you combine diet with prayer?","answer":"Well, it\u0027s funny how this thing started, Piers.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":768,"aSentId":769},{"question":"So what are the key things you have to do with this diet?","answer":"The number one thing -- you know, of course, diets are diets and health plans are health plans.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":801,"aSentId":802},{"question":"You drink alcohol?","answer":"No.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":833,"aSentId":834},{"question":"Never had (INAUDIBLE) nip, not even at Christmas?","answer":"Never have.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":836,"aSentId":837},{"question":"What would you say?","answer":"Well, the message of Christmas is that that babe in the manger didn\u0027t stay a babe in the manger.","docId":"121224pmt","qSentId":848,"aSentId":849}]